{"tid":1434710,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再諗邊個係鬼, 衝定唔衝","createTime":"2019-08-09T00:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T01:14:18.000Z","uid":56546,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"99b3510e2d068f72a0ac905a46cf1ff342926043","tid":1434710,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:41:21.000Z","msg":"對家只係求其係你地中間安插10個8個臥底<br />\n<br />\n你地就成班疑神疑鬼<br />\n日日諗邊個係鬼, 搞到散曬<br />\n結果就係中曬政府計<br />\n佢出你100份之1嘅人已經搞死你地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住我地每個人都係獨立個體<br />\n今次無大台, 自己就係自己個大台<br />\n唔好俾任何人影響自己信念<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當初出黎已經知道係要打長期戰<br />\n過程係攰, 精神一定處於緊張狀態<br />\n不過請唔好再分咩和理非同勇武<br />\n有手足決定要衝嘅<br />\n唔好譴責<br />\n要只守不攻嘅<br />\n亦係自己嘅自由<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日好多5毛已經揸住批評唔等於割蓆<br />\n不斷插我地伙記唔跟大隊意向黎影響佢地思想<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住：<br />\n做咗無人知結果<br />\n但唔行動就永遠無結果"},{"pid":"96cf007cbb0a9e40f83733b6a96b6520ed775d42","tid":1434710,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:42:29.000Z","msg":"Push一下"},{"pid":"a51a71c3a27306b19a9e67ea5587f49f4ac4b76c","tid":1434710,"uid":295664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:43:03.000Z","msg":"不譴責 不篤灰 不割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5816b0318af6eea55b6ef57e229d139bcd8c64fa","tid":1434710,"uid":55775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:43:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c082df738ec10e70b75ff6688a89aa5b2f4d7382","tid":1434710,"uid":56546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a51a71c3a27306b19a9e67ea5587f49f4ac4b76c","tid":1434710,"uid":295664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:43:03.000Z","msg":"不譴責 不篤灰 不割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:44:19.000Z","msg":"我地最大武器就係我地團結<br />\n同時間又獨立"},{"pid":"98c0436ffe78f5f2b421bc76778893c429f5f8f9","tid":1434710,"uid":302028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit